-festive-performance-at-london-st-pancras-3823798">这位音乐家在伦敦的圣潘克拉斯（St. Pancras）表现出了令人惊讶的表演，这位音乐家也使观众感到惊讶。</a>劳菲（Laufey）坐在钢琴上，对待围观者进行了一些曲目的现场演绎。</p><p>她演奏的歌曲中有节日经典，“冬季仙境”，随后是她的热门单曲“从Re Start”。她爆发的另一首曲目是《圣诞电影<i>红色》</i>中的歌曲“圣诞节魔术”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="劳菲（Laufey）现场表演埃拉·菲茨杰拉德（Ella Fitzgerald）的“何时或何时” | Bose X NME C24  - 在磁带上" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/NscYQ8fefXo?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>劳菲（Laufey）<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/laufey-28-08-2023-3488458">去年在NME上与<i>NME</i>进行封面</a>，分享了她通过音乐将爵士乐带入群众的梦想。</p><p>她告诉我们：“我一直对妈妈说，我记得我11岁时在车里时，&#39;我想为爵士音乐做<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）</a>为乡村音乐所做的事情。” “每天都有一项小成就，我觉得我越来越接近将爵士乐带回我这一代的目标。”</p><p> Last year, the musician took home the Grammy for Best Traditional Pop Vocal Album for her album, &#39;Bewitched&#39;.</p><p> In <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/laufey-bewitched-album-review-from-the-start-radar-3493926">a five-star review of the record</a> , <i>NME</i> described it as “confident and musically ambitious, melding jazz, pop and modern classical composition”.</p><p> “The Icelandic-Chinese star&#39;s second record &#39;Bewitched&#39; enchants in its own beautiful, unique way,” it read. “详细详细的管弦乐安排和她精湛的音乐性 - 多形的多人是一位备受赞誉的大提琴手，并在波士顿著名的伯克利音乐学院学习 - 支持她彻底的Z Ripostes。”</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/laufey-unleashes-her-inner-child-on-dreamy-new-love-song-silver-lining-3851647">Laufey unleashes her “inner child” on dreamy new love song &#39;Silver Lining&#39;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
